1.1.name: wordpress/embedly
1.1.description:
The Embedly plugin allows bloggers to embed videos, images, PDF, and article previews from "any" source with just the URL. It uses the Embedly API to get the embed code and display it in a post.

Write your post as normal and click the Embedly Icon in your Rich Editor to add "any" URL to your post.

OR

Embed 200+ sources by putting the URL to the content you want to embed on a single line like so:

This Embedly lets me embed everything great on the web!

http://twitpic.com/1owy89

http://i.imgur.com/ywzpg.jpg

http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B002BRZ9G0/ref=s9_pop_gw_ir01

http://twitter.com/jack/status/20
